
, Barack Obama's Twitter account (@BarackObama) is the eighth most popular official celebrity Twitter account.1 It is the official Twitter account for United States President Barack Obama (as designated by the verified icon next to his name), although he also tweets through @whitehouse. He has ranked at least as high as fourth in terms of followers.2 The account is &quot;run by #Obama2012 campaign staff. Tweets from the President are signed -bo.&quot;3 On May 24, 2012, Obama became the first President to respond to questions on Twitter.45
